<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer17383033161478608719"><i>Bruno Bettelheim</i> was an Austrian-born American child psychologist and writer. He gained an international reputation for his views on autism and for his claimed success in treating emotionally disturbed children.<br/><br/></span>

